text: Nikolsk () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnetatyshlinsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 25 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 1 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Nikolsk, Tatyshlinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
